[вњ”пёЏ] middleware/protect.js вЂ” JWT auth middleware
[вњ”пёЏ] routes/auth.js вЂ” POST /api/auth/register, POST /api/auth/login
[вњ”пёЏ] routes/jobs.js вЂ” GET, POST, PUT, DELETE /api/jobs
[вњ”пёЏ] Test all routes in Postman/Thunder Client

STEP 2 вЂ” FRONTEND
------------------
[вњ”пёЏ] cd .. && npm create vite@latest frontend
[вњ”пёЏ] Install dependencies (axios, zustand, react-router-dom, tailwindcss, daisyui)
[вњ”пёЏ] Setup Tailwind + DaisyUI
[вњ”пёЏ] Create folder structure (pages, components, store, lib)
[вњ”пёЏ] lib/axios.js вЂ” axios instance with baseURL
[вњ”пёЏ] store/useAuthStore.js вЂ” login, register, user state
[вњ”пёЏ] store/useJobStore.js вЂ” jobs CRUD state
[вњ”пёЏ] pages/Login.jsx
[вњ”пёЏ] pages/Register.jsx
[ ] pages/Dashboard.jsx вЂ” spreadsheet table
[ ] components/JobRow.jsx вЂ” single editable row
[ ] components/AddJobModal.jsx вЂ” manual add form
[ ] components/EditJobModal.jsx вЂ” edit form
[ ] App.jsx вЂ” routes + protected route
[ ] Test full flow (register в†’ login в†’ add/edit/delete jobs)

STEP 3 вЂ” EXTENSION
-------------------
[ ] cd .. && mkdir extension
[ ] Create manifest.json (Manifest V3)
[ ] Install React + Vite for popup UI
[ ] popup/App.jsx вЂ” main popup component
[ ] popup/main.jsx вЂ” entry point
[ ] background.js вЂ” service worker
[ ] Read current tab URL + title using chrome.tabs API
[ ] Parse company name + job title from page title
[ ] Read JWT from dashboard site localStorage via content script
[ ] POST job to backend with JWT
[ ] Show success / error state in popup
[ ] Build popup (vite build)
[ ] Test extension in chrome://extensions (developer mode)

STEP 4 вЂ” CONNECT & POLISH
--------------------------
[ ] Test extension в†’ backend в†’ dashboard full flow
[ ] Handle duplicate URL (same job applied twice)
[ ] Add status filter on dashboard (All / Applied / Saved / Interviewing / Offer / Rejected)
[ ] Add date sort (newest first)
[ ] Deploy backend to Render
[ ] Deploy frontend to Vercel
[ ] Update extension manifest with production API URL
[ ] Final test on LinkedIn, Indeed, any job site




